           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Fort Lauderdale suburbs top list with most $200K homes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Story at a glance Fort Lauderdale, Fla. topped the list of U.S. cities with the most available homes under $200,000. A new Realtor.com report noted that due to the COVID-19 pandemic, real estate prices skyrocketed nationwide and largely have yet to drop back down. The average U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/19/fort-lauderdale-suburbs-top-list-with-most-200k-homes/"  >(Lauren Irwin, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:05:17 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:05:17 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
