           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">U.S. couple among hundreds who died in pilgrimage to Mecca</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A couple from Maryland were among the more than 1,300 people who died during the Hajj pilgrimage in Saudi Arabia, Democratic Senate candidate Angela Alsobrooks announced Sunday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/24/couple-among-hundreds-who-died-in-pilgrimage-to-mecca/"  >(Nick Robertson, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
