  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/25/israeli-high-court-rules-ultra-orthodox.webp" alt="Israeli court rules ultra-Orthodox men must serve in military"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israeli court rules ultra-Orthodox men must serve in military</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israeli’s high court ruled Tuesday that ultra-Orthodox men must be drafted for compulsory military service, a major shift that could break up Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu’s government.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/25/israeli-high-court-rules-ultra-orthodox/"  >(Nick Robertson, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:38:13 +0000">
