           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Alberto downgraded to tropical depression after dumping inches of rain on South Texas border</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tropical Storm Alberto came ashore around 8 a.m. CT on Thursday near Tampico, Mexico, after dumping several inches of rain on the South Texas border and Gulf Coast areas.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/21/alberto-downgraded-to-tropical-depression-after-dumping-inches-of-rain-on-south-texas-border/"  >(Sandra Sanchez, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
