           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Russia bans 81 media organizations in response to EU restrictions</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Russian government banned 81 European media organizations Tuesday, continuing a crackdown on information access amidst the country’s invasion of Ukraine.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/25/russia-bans-81-media-organizations-eu-restrictions/"  >(Nick Robertson, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:17:15 +0000">
