      <img src="/static8/tech/2024/06/26/tesla-is-recalling-the-cybertruck-due-to-issues-with-the-windshield-and-trunk-bed-trim.webp" alt="Tesla is recalling the Cybertruck due to issues with the windshield and trunk bed trim"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tesla is recalling the Cybertruck due to issues with the windshield and trunk bed trim</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tesla once again is issuing a physical recall for its Cybertruck. 
Tesla is calling back 11,688 of its electric trucks due to a faulty front windshield wiper that could make it hard for the driver to see in certain conditions.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/26/tesla-is-recalling-the-cybertruck-due-to-issues-with-the-windshield-and-trunk-bed-trim/"  >(Jessica Bursztynsky, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:35:46 +0000">
