           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tesla recalls Cybertrucks twice in a day to fix windshield wipers, loose trim</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The company estimates in the filings that 2% of the pickups may have defective wiper motors, and that 1% may need trim pieces replaced or reworked.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/25/tesla-recalls-cybertrucks-twice-in-one-day-to-fix-windshield-wipers-detaching-trim/"  >(Bloomberg, The Mercury News)</a>
