           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">UN Launches Global Principles to Combat Online Hate, Demands Big Tech Action</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The United Nations Chief launches global principles to combat online hate and lies, demanding big tech companies take action to reduce harm caused to people and societies worldwide.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/24/un-launches-global-principles-to-combat-online-hate-and-demands-big-tech-take-action-now/"  >(EDITH M. LEDERER, Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
