           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US investigates China Mobile, China Telecom, and China Unicom over data misuse concerns</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The US has launched investigations into China Mobile, China Telecom, and China Unicom amid concerns that these firms could misuse their access to US data, according to a Reuters report.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/25/us-investigates-china-mobile-china-telecom-and-china-unicom-over-data-misuse-concerns/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
