    <h3 itemprop="headline">Swimming at SoFi? New L.A. 2028 Olympics venues announced</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      With the 2024 Paris Summer Olympic Games nearly here, it's never too early for Southern Californians to start planning for 2028.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/21/venues-for-the-los-angeles-2028-olympics-announced-and-there-are-some-major-surprises/"  >(Austin Turner, KTLA 5)</a>
