    <h3 itemprop="headline">Knicks set to acquire Mikal Bridges in a trade from the Brooklyn Nets, AP sources say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (AP) — Mikal Bridges is being traded by the Brooklyn Nets to the New York Knicks, where he will join Jalen Brunson and his other former Villanova teammates, two people with knowledge of the details said Tuesday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/26/knicks-set-to-acquire-mikal-bridges-in-a-trade-from-the-brooklyn-nets-ap-sources-say/"  >(BRIAN MAHONEY, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
