           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sheri Biggs wins Republican nod for US House in South Carolina over Trump-backed candidate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      COLUMBIA, S.C. (AP) — Sheri Biggs, a nurse practitioner and Air National Guard officer, won the Republican nomination for the U.S. House in South Carolina’s 3rd District on Tuesday, defeating a challenger who called himself former President Donald Trump's pastor.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/26/sheri-biggs-wins-republican-nod-for-us-house-in-south-carolina-over-trump-backed-candidate/"  >(JEFFREY COLLINS, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:00:19 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:00:19 +0000">
