    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lexi Lonas, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/24/civil-liberties-groups-file-lawsuit-against-louisiana-ten-commandment-law.webp" alt="Civil liberties groups file lawsuit against Louisiana Ten Commandments law"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Civil liberties groups file lawsuit against Louisiana Ten Commandments law</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A coalition of civil liberties groups on Monday filed a lawsuit against Louisiana after its governor last week signed a bill requiring that the Ten Commandments be displayed in every public school classroom starting in 2025.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/24/civil-liberties-groups-file-lawsuit-against-louisiana-ten-commandment-law/"  >(Lexi Lonas, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
