           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Republican Jeff Hurd beats election denier boosted by Democrats in race for Boebert seat</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Establishment-backed Republican candidate Jeff Hurd has won his GOP primary for Rep. Lauren Boebert’s (R-Colo.) seat in Colorado’s 3rd Congressional District, according to a projection from Decision Desk HQ.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/26/republican-jeff-hurd-beats-election-denier-boosted-by-democrats-in-race-for-boebert-seat/"  >(Caroline Vakil, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
